synopsis.value: Unfortunate gnome's dialog after the goblin hunt celebration party. There are actually two different dialoues: one for when the player sided with the goblins, in which he is pissed off at the player and ready to leave, and one where the player sided with the tieflings, in which he is happy for them, but doesn't want to partake in the celebrations himself, since it has nothing to do with him, and he wants to go save his friend as soon as possible. In this case, he's standing next to a workbench, working on making explosive arrows.
